    "author": "",
    "translated": false,
    "body": "<h1>Nicknames Fans Use</h1>\n<p>In Chinese fan culture, nicknames often express closeness rather than ridicule. Here are the most beloved ones:</p>\n<h2>小胖 (Xiǎo Pàng) - &quot;Little Fatty&quot;</h2>\n<h3>The &quot;Xiao Pang&quot; Dilemma</h3>\n<p>⚠️ <strong>Important Cultural Context:</strong> This might sound offensive in English, but it&#39;s actually a term of endearment!</p>\n<p>In Chinese culture, calling someone &quot;Little Fatty&quot; is affectionate, not body shaming. It represents:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Being cute and cherubic</li>\n<li>Looking well-fed and healthy  </li>\n<li>His adorable round face when he was younger</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>It&#39;s how fans express their love for his cute appearance!</strong> 🥰</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>东哥 (Dōng Gē) - &quot;Brother Dong&quot;</h2>\n<p>A respectful yet familiar way to address him, showing admiration while maintaining closeness. &quot;Ge&quot; (哥) means &quot;older brother&quot; and is commonly used to show respect to male figures you admire.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>The Violence Panda 🐼💥</h2>\n<p><strong>Origin:</strong> Coined by international commentators</p>\n<p><strong>Why:</strong> &quot;He looks cuddly like a panda, but plays with ferocious power.&quot;</p>\n<p><em>Deceptively cute, incredibly dangerous.</em></p>\n<p>This nickname perfectly captures the contrast between his gentle appearance and explosive playing style.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>铁血一单 (Tiě Xuè Yī Dān) - &quot;Iron-Blooded No.1 Singles&quot;</h2>\n<p>Refers to his unwavering determination as China&#39;s top singles player for over a decade. &quot;Iron-blooded&quot; (铁血) conveys:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Unyielding spirit</li>\n<li>Warrior-like determination</li>\n<li>Never backing down under pressure</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>Other Nicknames</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>樊百万 (Fán Bǎi Wàn)</strong> - &quot;Fan Million&quot; - For his WTT Grand Smash victories</li>\n<li><strong>中国长城 (Zhōngguó Chángchéng)</strong> - &quot;The Wall of China&quot; - For his impenetrable defense</li>\n<li><strong>Kaiser Fan</strong> - His Bundesliga nickname in Germany</li>\n</ul>\n"
