    "body": "<h2>【全场回顾】2024年巴黎奥运会乒乓球男单1/4决赛 樊振东VS张本智和</h2>\n<p>强烈建议打开弹幕观看！</p>\n<iframe src=\"https://fzd-fans.com//player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV1a9KczoEZi&autoplay=0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"500\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe><hr>\n<h2>樊振东全运会男单卫冕！一口气看完</h2>\n<iframe src=\"https://fzd-fans.com//player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV1VQCiBiEUs&autoplay=0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"500\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe><hr>\n<h2>【樊振东】麦霸熊猫！翻唱合集</h2>\n<iframe src=\"https://fzd-fans.com//player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV1wA411P7TQ&p=24&autoplay=0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"500\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe><hr>\n<h2>八一之心 人生百态</h2>\n<iframe src=\"https://fzd-fans.com//player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV17rhHzXEQE&autoplay=0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"500\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe><hr>\n<h2>【樊振东】2017年生贺视频 原创歌曲《一路同行》</h2>\n<iframe src=\"https://fzd-fans.com//player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV1g4411g7UF&autoplay=0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"500\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe><hr>\n<p><em>未完待续...(欢迎投稿/推荐，请发送邮件至 <a href=\"mailto:kkjusdoit@gmail.com\">kkjusdoit@gmail.com（点击复制）</a>）</em></p>\n"
