    "author": "",
    "translated": true,
    "body": "<h1>Yan An Congratulates Fan Zhendong on World Championship Victory</h1>\n<p>In 2021, former Chinese national team player Yan An released a congratulatory video for Fan Zhendong, featuring <em>Lonely Warrior</em> as the background music.</p>\n<h2>Video</h2>\n<iframe src=\"https://fzd-fans.com//player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV1zM4y1P78p&autoplay=0\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16/9;\"></iframe><p><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1zM4y1P78p/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click&vd_source=293654ead1a645563567c0921dfd3ac2\">Original Bilibili Video</a></p>\n<hr>\n"
